              <tr><td><strong>Auto-generated content</strong></td><td>Programmatic pages with no human editorial judgment</td><td>Noindex or rewrite with substance</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>Low-quality UGC</strong></td><td>User-generated comments or posts with spam or no value</td><td>Moderate or noindex thin UGC sections</td></tr>
            </tbody>
